Sterling Investment Management, Inc. Buys Berkshire Hathaway Inc, McDonald's Corp, Sells ...


January 23, 2017, 04:38:02 PM EDT
By insider, GuruFocus









































Shutterstock photo


Sterling Investment Management, Inc.New Purchases: MCD ,Added Positions: BRK.B , PG ,Reduced Positions:BRK.A, MO, MSFT, CMCSA, AAPL, CSCO, VZ, PM, PFE, BAC,Sold Out:RYAAY,For the details of Sterling Investment Management, Inc.'s stock buys and sells, go to http://www.gurufocus.com/StockBuy.php?GuruName=Sterling+Investment+Management%2C+Inc.These are the top 5 holdings of Sterling Investment Management, Inc.Berkshire Hathaway Inc (BRK.B) - 56,734 shares, 13.2% of the total portfolio. Shares added by 37.12%Microsoft Corp ( MSFT ) - 51,282 shares, 4.55% of the total portfolio. Shares reduced by 3.14%Altria Group Inc ( MO ) - 45,711 shares, 4.41% of the total portfolio. Shares reduced by 3.34%Apple Inc ( AAPL ) - 26,273 shares, 4.35% of the total portfolio. Shares reduced by 2.96%Comcast Corp ( CMCSA ) - 44,039 shares, 4.34% of the total portfolio. Shares reduced by 3.23%New Purchase: McDonald's Corp ( MCD )Sterling Investment Management, Inc. initiated holdings in McDonald's Corp. The purchase prices were between $110.57 and $123.72, with an estimated average price of $117.26. The stock is now traded at around $121.38. The impact to the portfolio due to this purchase was 1.9%. The holdings were 10,950 shares as of 2016-12-31.Added: Berkshire Hathaway Inc (BRK.B)Sterling Investment Management, Inc. added to the holdings in Berkshire Hathaway Inc by 37.12%. The purchase prices were between $142.95 and $166.62, with an estimated average price of $153.96. The stock is now traded at around $159.00. The impact to the portfolio due to this purchase was 3.57%. The holdings were 56,734 shares as of 2016-12-31.Sold Out: Ryanair Holdings PLC (RYAAY)Sterling Investment Management, Inc. sold out the holdings in Ryanair Holdings PLC. The sale prices were between $67.79 and $84.81, with an estimated average price of $78.72.Warning! GuruFocus has detected 4 Warning Sign with BRK.B. Click here to check it out.BRK.B 15-Year Financial DataThe intrinsic value of BRK.BPeter Lynch Chart of 